<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Oops! Route Not Found</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;800&family=JetBrains+Mono&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f8fafc;
        --card: #ffffff;
        --text: #1e293b;
        --primary: #6366f1;
        --secondary: #f1f5f9;
        --border: #e2e8f0;
        --accent: #f43f5e;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body {
        background-color: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }

      /* Floating Illustration Area */
      .icon-box {
        font-size: 64px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes float {
        0%,
        100% {
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateY(-10px);
        }
      }

      h1 {
        font-weight: 800;
        font-size: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: var(--text);
      }
      p {
        color: #64748b;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      /* The Main Card */
      .card {
        background: var(--card);
        border: 2px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 12px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        color: #94a3b8;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: left;
      }

      /* Route Links Grid */
      .routes-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .route-link {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 12px;
        background: var(--secondary);
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: all 0.2s;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
      }

      .route-link:hover {
        background: #eff6ff;
        border-color: var(--primary);
        color: var(--primary);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .route-link span {
        background: white;
        padding: 2px 6px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 10px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      /* Action Buttons */
      .back-btn {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 14px;
        background: var(--text);
        color: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 10px;
        transition: opacity 0.2s;
      }

      .back-btn:hover {
        opacity: 0.9;
      }

      .footer-note {
        margin-top: 24px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #94a3b8;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="icon-box">🗺️</div>
      <h1>Lost in Space?</h1>
      <p>Humne dhundne ki koshish ki, magar ye page kahi nahi mila.</p>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="section-title">Quick Redirect to Routes</div>

        <div class="routes-grid">
          <a href="/api/v1/person" class="route-link">
            <span>GET</span> /person
          </a>
          <a href="/api/v1/food" class="route-link"> <span>GET</span> /food </a>
          <a href="/api/v1/vehicle" class="route-link">
            <span>GET</span> /vehicle
          </a>
          <a href="/api/v1/commerce" class="route-link">
            <span>GET</span> /commerce
          </a>
          <a href="/api/v1/music" class="route-link">
            <span>GET</span> /music
          </a>
          <a href="/api/v1/animals" class="route-link">
            <span>GET</span> /animals
          </a>
        </div>

        <a href="/" class="back-btn">Go to Home Page</a>
      </div>

      <div class="footer-note">PracticeAPI v1.0 • Built with ❤️</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
